<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I am sure plenty of 14 year olds have read this book through out the ages. Especially during the 1920s and 1930s there were probably plenty of young r<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I am sure plenty of 14 year olds have read this book through out the ages. Especially during the 1920s and 1930s there were probably plenty of young readers since this was a popular memoir at the time. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
