<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18693396-poilu"><img alt="Poilu: The World War I Notebooks of Corporal Louis Barthas, Barrelmaker, 1914-1918" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1387770798l/18693396._SX98_.jpg" />
